        "ja": "Pinned 転送は H2D 約 52.42 GiB/s、D2H 約 52.13 GiB/s まで到達し、PCIe 5.0 x16 の片方向理論値 63.015 GB/s を GiB/s 換算した約 58.69 GiB/s に対しておよそ 89% 前後だった。",
        "en": "Pinned transfers reached about 52.42 GiB/s for H2D and 52.13 GiB/s for D2H, which is roughly 89% of the one-way PCIe 5.0 x16 theoretical limit after converting 63.015 GB/s into about 58.69 GiB/s."
      },
      {
        "ja": "Pageable 転送は H2D 約 19.41 GiB/s、D2H 約 15.39 GiB/s にとどまり、理論値比では 26〜33% 程度だった。今回の大きな差は PCIe リンク帯域不足よりも pageable 転送経路の追加 overhead を示唆している。",
        "en": "Pageable transfers stayed at about 19.41 GiB/s for H2D and 15.39 GiB/s for D2H, or only around 26-33% of the theoretical limit. The large gap in this run points more to extra overhead in the pageable transfer path than to insufficient PCIe link bandwidth."
      },
      {
        "ja": "Pinned と pageable の差はサイズと方向により変動したが、最大では約 4.54x まで開いた。Pageable 側で内部 staging buffer と追加コピーが発生している可能性が高い。",
        "en": "The gap between pinned and pageable varied by size and direction, but reached about 4.54x at maximum. A likely explanation is the use of an internal staging buffer and extra copies on the pageable path."
